    "In this section we report basic descriptive facts about who uses consumer ChatGPT.",
    "Existing work documents variation in generative AI use by demographic groups within representative samples in the U.S. (Bick et al. (2024), Hartley et al.",
    "(2025)) and within a subset of occupations in Denmark (Humlum and Vestergaard, 2025a).",
    "All of these papers find that generative AI is used more frequently by men, young people, and those with tertiary and/or graduate education.",
    "We make three contributions relative to this prior literature."
